The paper discusses the application of data mining techniques to web usage log repositories to discover usage patterns, which falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of fuzzy c-means clustering, which is a machine learning algorithm and falls under the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with preprocessing and analyzing large amounts of data, which falls under the categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) and Cybersecurity (cs.CY). Finally, the paper deals with the management and analysis of data, which falls under the category of Databases (cs.DB).
